Description.enUS:
Support air unit. Can restore Void energy to friendly units. Can use Disappearance to cloak allies.

Can attack ground and air units.

Tooltip.enUS: Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
Tooltip.ruRU: Приказать выбранным боевым единицам двигаться в указанную точку или следовать за указанной целью. При этом они не будут вступать в бой с возможным противником.

Tooltip.enUS: Orders selected units to cancel all orders and stop moving.
Tooltip.ruRU: Приказать выбранным боевым единицам прекратить выполнение всех задач и остановиться.

Tooltip.enUS: Orders selected units to stay where they are and attack enemies that are within range. Units will neither chase down enemies nor move to engage.
Tooltip.ruRU: Приказать выбранным боевым единицам оставаться на месте и атаковать противника в зоне досягаемости, при этом не преследуя его и не приближаясь к нему, чтобы вступить в бой.

Tooltip.enUS: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Tooltip.ruRU: Приказать выбранным боевым единицам двигаться в выбранную точку, вступая в бой с противниками, которые встретятся по пути. Указав в качестве цели конкретную боевую единицу, вы прикажете атаковать ее до уничтожения.

Tooltip.enUS: Orders selected units to patrol between their current position and the target area. Units will attack enemies and move to engage nearby enemies.
Tooltip.ruRU: Приказать выбранным боевым единицам курсировать между текущей позицией и выбранной точкой. Обнаружив противника, они будут приближаться на расстояние атаки и вступать в бой.

Tooltip.enUS: List of Hybrid air support units.
List of Hybrid air battle units.
List of Hybrid ground units.
Creates a cloak aura around the Energator. All units in range are cloaked for 4.2 second,seconds.
Restores up to 11 Void energy per second. Every 0.5 Void restored drains 1 Energy.
Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS:
Weapon damage deals splash damage, gains increased range.

Each attack costs 25 Void energy.

Creates a wandering Tornado at target point for 12.6 seconds. Tornado deals 16 damage per second.

Doesn't affect structures.
**Chimera** burrows to target location within Void power field.
Sentinel jumps behind enemy target dealing 15 damage. If target is a unit, also stuns them for 1.4 second.**Stun ignores Massive targets**
Weapon deals base damage with base range and without Void energy cost.

Warps spacetime within the target area for 7.0 seconds. All **enemy ground units** within the field are time stopped, unabled to act and revealed.

Massive units will shatter time warp on contact.
Makes enemy units take 50% increased damage from all sources and makes their weapons do 50% less damage for 14 seconds.

Unleashes a traveling Psionic Orb that deals up to 40 to each enemy along its path.

Same enemy can be damaged every 0.38 seconds.
Deals 10 Damage to each non-structure enemy nearby and restore 7 life or Protection shield per each enemy hit upon activatation and every 1.40 second during 5.60 seconds.
Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Spirit self-destructs and provides vision of target enemy unit or structure for 60 seconds, revealing them.
Restores up to 11 Void energy per second. Every 0.5 Void restored drains 1 Energy.
Creates a cloak aura around the Energator. All units in range are cloaked for 4.2 second,seconds.
Target structure or unit is phased out of existence for 14 seconds. It cannot be attacked, use abilities and provide power.**Massive and heroic targets are immune**

Create empowered Void power field. Units and structures in power field regenerate their Protection shield even if they are in combat and their Void energy regen rate is increased by 200%.

While channeling, Conductor can not use abilities or move.
Reverts Conductor back to Moveable Mode, allowing it to move.
Unloads all units.
After preparation for 4 seconds Navigator teleports to any Player unit.
Drops the current order without performing it, and allows you to select a different order.
Tooltip.ruRU: Отменить текущий приказ и отдать следующий.

Tooltip.enUS: Psyon increases its movespeed by 250% for 7 seconds.

Cloaks the unit, preventing enemy units from seeing or attacking it. A cloaked unit will only be revealed by detectors or effects.

Drains 7.1 Void energy per second.
Decloaks the selected unit, making it visible to enemies.
**Shapeshifter** deals high damage against single **armored** units without Void energy cost.
**Shapeshifter** deals splash damage, but each attack costs 20 Void energy.
**Shapeshifter** prepares for 2.00 seconds. After that all air targets in an area becomes grounded, making them unabled to act and vulerable for ground attacks for 8.40 seconds.
Weapon deals base damage with base range and without Void energy cost.

Weapon ignores armor and its range is increased by 6.00, but damage is decreased by 2.

Weapon drains 0 Void energy per attack.
Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
